sql_query.sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT 1 AS one FROM "categories" WHERE ((FALSE AND LENGTH(COALESCE(email_in, '')) > 0 AND email_in_allow_strangers)
          OR categories.id NOT IN (SELECT category_id FROM category_groups)
          OR categories.id IN (
                SELECT category_id
                  FROM category_groups
                 WHERE permission_type IN (1)
                   AND (group_id = 0 OR group_id IN (SELECT group_id FROM group_users WHERE user_id = 3))
             )) LIMIT 1) subquery_for_count

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT 1 AS one FROM "categories" WHERE ((FALSE AND LENGTH(COALESCE(email_in, '')) > 0 AND email_in_allow_strangers)
          OR categories.id NOT IN (SELECT category_id FROM category_groups)
          OR categories.id IN (
                SELECT category_id
                  FROM category_groups
                 WHERE permission_type IN (1)
                   AND (group_id = 0 OR group_id IN (SELECT group_id FROM group_users WHERE user_id = 3))
             )) LIMIT 1) subquery_for_count

          OR categories.id NOT IN (SELECT category_id FROM category_groups)

sql_query.sql:
SELECT a.attname, format_type(a.atttypid, a.atttypmod),
       pg_get_expr(d.adbin, d.adrelid), a.attnotnull, a.atttypid, a.atttypmod,
       c.collname, col_description(a.attrelid, a.attnum) AS comment
  FROM pg_attribute a
  LEFT JOIN pg_attrdef d ON a.attrelid = d.adrelid AND a.attnum = d.adnum
  LEFT JOIN pg_type t ON a.atttypid = t.oid
  LEFT JOIN pg_collation c ON a.attcollation = c.oid AND a.attcollation <> t.typcollation
 WHERE a.attrelid = '"posts"'::regclass
   AND a.attnum > 0 AND NOT a.attisdropped
 ORDER BY a.attnum
UPDATE "posts" SET spam_count = 1 WHERE ("posts"."deleted_at" IS NULL) AND "posts"."id" = 193

sql_query.sql:
SELECT a.attname, format_type(a.atttypid, a.atttypmod),
       pg_get_expr(d.adbin, d.adrelid), a.attnotnull, a.atttypid, a.atttypmod,
       c.collname, col_description(a.attrelid, a.attnum) AS comment
  FROM pg_attribute a
  LEFT JOIN pg_attrdef d ON a.attrelid = d.adrelid AND a.attnum = d.adnum
  LEFT JOIN pg_type t ON a.atttypid = t.oid
  LEFT JOIN pg_collation c ON a.attcollation = c.oid AND a.attcollation <> t.typcollation
 WHERE a.attrelid = '"posts"'::regclass
   AND a.attnum > 0 AND NOT a.attisdropped
 ORDER BY a.attnum
UPDATE "posts" SET off_topic_count = 1 WHERE ("posts"."deleted_at" IS NULL) AND "posts"."id" = 194

SELECT a.attname, format_type(a.atttypid, a.atttypmod),
       pg_get_expr(d.adbin, d.adrelid), a.attnotnull, a.atttypid, a.atttypmod,
       c.collname, col_description(a.attrelid, a.attnum) AS comment
  FROM pg_attribute a
  LEFT JOIN pg_attrdef d ON a.attrelid = d.adrelid AND a.attnum = d.adnum
  LEFT JOIN pg_type t ON a.atttypid = t.oid
  LEFT JOIN pg_collation c ON a.attcollation = c.oid AND a.attcollation <> t.typcollation
 WHERE a.attrelid = '"posts"'::regclass
   AND a.attnum > 0 AND NOT a.attisdropped
 ORDER BY a.attnum

sql_query.sql:
SELECT a.attname, format_type(a.atttypid, a.atttypmod),
       pg_get_expr(d.adbin, d.adrelid), a.attnotnull, a.atttypid, a.atttypmod,
       c.collname, col_description(a.attrelid, a.attnum) AS comment
  FROM pg_attribute a
  LEFT JOIN pg_attrdef d ON a.attrelid = d.adrelid AND a.attnum = d.adnum
  LEFT JOIN pg_type t ON a.atttypid = t.oid
  LEFT JOIN pg_collation c ON a.attcollation = c.oid AND a.attcollation <> t.typcollation
 WHERE a.attrelid = '"posts"'::regclass
   AND a.attnum > 0 AND NOT a.attisdropped
 ORDER BY a.attnum
UPDATE "posts" SET spam_count = 1 WHERE ("posts"."deleted_at" IS NULL) AND "posts"."id" = 193

SELECT a.attname, format_type(a.atttypid, a.atttypmod),
       pg_get_expr(d.adbin, d.adrelid), a.attnotnull, a.atttypid, a.atttypmod,
       c.collname, col_description(a.attrelid, a.attnum) AS comment
  FROM pg_attribute a
  LEFT JOIN pg_attrdef d ON a.attrelid = d.adrelid AND a.attnum = d.adnum
  LEFT JOIN pg_type t ON a.atttypid = t.oid
  LEFT JOIN pg_collation c ON a.attcollation = c.oid AND a.attcollation <> t.typcollation
 WHERE a.attrelid = '"posts"'::regclass
   AND a.attnum > 0 AND NOT a.attisdropped
 ORDER BY a.attnum
UPDATE "posts" SET off_topic_count = 1 WHERE ("posts"."deleted_at" IS NULL) AND "posts"."id" = 194

SELECT a.attname, format_type(a.atttypid, a.atttypmod),
       pg_get_expr(d.adbin, d.adrelid), a.attnotnull, a.atttypid, a.atttypmod,
       c.collname, col_description(a.attrelid, a.attnum) AS comment
  FROM pg_attribute a
  LEFT JOIN pg_attrdef d ON a.attrelid = d.adrelid AND a.attnum = d.adnum
  LEFT JOIN pg_type t ON a.atttypid = t.oid
  LEFT JOIN pg_collation c ON a.attcollation = c.oid AND a.attcollation <> t.typcollation
 WHERE a.attrelid = '"posts"'::regclass
   AND a.attnum > 0 AND NOT a.attisdropped
 ORDER BY a.attnum
